Create a program Laptop Usage System (Functions Version)

Data Types:
brand (string), ram (int), storage (int), battery (float), is_on (boolean)

Functions:
turn_on(is_on) → set to True
turn_off(is_on) → set to False
use_laptop(battery, hours) → decrease battery (1 hour = 10%)
charge_laptop(battery, amount) → increase battery but not above 100
get_info(brand, ram, storage, battery, is_on) → return laptop info
